ext17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012005, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "It is advisable to observe fasting on this day. According to narrations, Prophet Noah (a) embarked on the Ark on such a day; he therefore ordered his companions to observe fasting. Hence, whoever observes fasting on this day, Hellfire will move away from him for a distance of one year walking.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mustahab hai keh is din roza rakkhe. Riwaayat hai keh Hazrat Nooh (a) is din kashti mein sawaar huwe aur apne saathiyo’n ko roza rakhne ka hukm diya, pas jo shakhs is din roza rakkhe to Jahannam ki aag se ek saal ki masaafat (walking distance) par rahega.", "UrduDescription": "یہ بڑی عظمت والا دن ہے : روزہ رکھنا، روایت میں ہے کہ حضرت نوح ؑاسی دن کشتی پر سوار ہوئے اور آپؑ نے اپنے ساتھیوں کو روزہ رکھنے کا حکم دیا لہٰذا جو شخص اس دن کا روزہ رکھے تو جہنم کی آگ اس سے ایک سال کی مسافت کے برابر دور رہے گی۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueS